<br>
Additional info gleaned from talking to Mythic folks at their booth:<br>
<br>
They will be expanding all dungeons.<br>
<br>
There will be underwater zones in the expansion (Shrouded Isles).<br>
<br>
There will be 5-10 new outdoor zones in the expansion.<br>
